name: CubeWorld (PrinceAliSaga)
description:
Make your way trough an ever changing world of cubes by solving puzzle of increasing difficulty. In this world cubes rule all. Fit them in the right place to proceed with your journey. Compete to get the best scores possible.

You will have to think outside the box to solve all 10 levels. Will you be able to make it, will you succeed and reach the end? Will you make it in this land of cubes. in this cubeworld!

Controls

Arrows  to move

R button to restart.

Developer

Ali "PrinceAliSaga" Sagayeva / Dudayev
